Maintainer:  None <fink-devel@lists.sourceforge.net>
License: OSI-Approved
Homepage: http://code.google.com/p/dictionnaire-le-littre/
BuildDepends: <<
	libiconv-dev, 
	libpng16,
	qt4-base-mac (>= 4.7.3-1)
<<
